@startuml C3_Register_ShippingAgents_Physical_View
title C3 â€“ Register Shipping Agents (Physical View)
left to right direction

skinparam node {
  BackgroundColor White
  BorderColor Black
  FontColor Black
}
skinparam artifact {
  BackgroundColor HoneyDew
  BorderColor Black
  FontColor Black
}

node "Shipping Agents Management API\n(ASP.NET Core Application)" as API {
  artifact "TodoApi.Controllers.dll" as Controllers
  artifact "TodoApi.Application.Services.dll" as AppServices
  artifact "TodoApi.Application.Mapping.dll" as Mapping
  artifact "TodoApi.Domain.Repositories.dll" as DomainRepos
  artifact "TodoApi.Infrastructure.Data.dll" as InfraData
  artifact "EFCore.dll" as EFCore
  artifact "Program.cs / Startup.cs" as Startup
}

node "Runtime Environment\n(.NET 8 SDK / Docker Container)" as Runtime {
  artifact "ASP.NET Core Hosting" as Hosting
}

database "PLMS Database\n(SQL / EF Core)" as DB
cloud "Email / SMS Providers\n(SMTP / API)" as Notif

Hosting --> API : Hosts the ASP.NET Core application
Controllers --> AppServices : Calls ShippingAgentService
AppServices --> Mapping : Uses ShippingAgentMapper
AppServices --> DomainRepos : Uses IShippingAgentRepository
DomainRepos --> InfraData : Implemented via PortContext
InfraData --> EFCore : ORM
API --> DB : Connection String / EF Core
API --> Notif : Sends email / SMS notifications
Startup --> Hosting : Configuration and startup
@enduml
